    "These applications range from automated abstract generation to enhancing the fluency of English prose for non-native speakers and even streamlining the creation of exhaustive literature reviews [6, 7].",
    "However, AI output is far from being perfect, as AI hallucination has been well described and documented in the current literature [8, 9].",
    "Additional concerns include ethical, copyright, transparency, and legal issues, the risk of bias, plagiarism, lack of originality, limited knowledge, incorrect citations, cybersecurity issues, and the risk of infodemics [9].",
